            "body": "This suggestion makes no sense.\r\n\r\nI would expect it to work like this:\r\n\r\n1. do an edit\r\n2. repeat it a few times with dot\r\n3. expand some fold\r\n4. continue repeating the edit with dot\r\n\r\nFor the unfold action to take over the last-saved-edit which dot repeats is ludicrous. \r\n\r\n- https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12566235/what-can-the-dot-command-repeat-exactly\r\n",
